org.hl7.types
Interface Numeric

All Known Subinterfaces:
INT, REAL
All Known Implementing Classes:
INTlongAdapter, INTninf, INTnull, INTpinf, REALdoubleAdapter, REALninf, REALnull, REALpinf
public interface Numeric

This interface is defined to plug in a bunch of methods useful in Java. These methods are like the methods that use HL7 types as arguments, but they use Java builtins. That way we can speed up some work and it's easier for the programmer since they can use Java literals for those builtins.
